snippet.title: DEPP vs HEARD VERDICT REACHED! Discussion about trial and MORE!
snippet.description: A verdict has been reached with Amber Heard and Johnny Depp! Heard vs Depp in the UK has officially come out with a verdict! Crazy!!! Disclaimer: This video operated under the impression that the viewer was aware that a verdict has been reached. I had and have no intention of making it appear that we are "aware" of what the verdict itself is. All we know is that a verdict has been decided, but we are unsure of what that specific verdict is, until Monday.
